@startuml
!include <C4/C4_Context>
title Shop Platform Context with Notes

Person(user, "Customer", "Buys products online")
System(shop, "Shop Platform", "The core system in scope")
System(inventory, "Inventory System", "Tracks stock levels")
System_Ext(payments, "Payment Gateway", "Processes card payments")
System_Ext(email, "Email Service", "Sends transactional email")

Rel(user, shop, "Places orders via", "HTTPS")
Rel(shop, payments, "Charges cards via", "HTTPS")
Rel(shop, email, "Sends receipts via", "SMTP")
Rel(shop, inventory, "Checks stock via", "gRPC")

' Scope: shop

' right/left/top-of single-anchor notes. PlantUML's `top of` maps to `over`,
' which nudge places ABOVE the anchor (non-occluding) rather than covering it.
note right of shop : Handles the full<br/>checkout journey
note left of payments : Legacy provider,<br/>being retired
note top of inventory : Owned by Team Phoenix
@enduml
